This project contains also code/data from other projects:

* The icon is taken from the Oxygen-Iconset, available under GNU LGPLv3: http://www.oxygen-icons.org/
* osmfilter, osmconvert, osmupdate from Markus Weber, available under GNU GPLv3: http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Osmfilter
* osm2pgsql, available under GPLv2: http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Osm2pgsql
* some functions in renderer/vtiler.php are PHP-rewritten and modified functions from twms, available under Do What The Fuck You Want To Public License: https://code.google.com/p/twms/
* some functions in renderer/vtiler.php are PHP-rewritten and modified functions from Kothic, available under GNU GPLv3: https://code.google.com/p/kothic/

ATTENTION: The included binaries can only be used on i386 Linux systems. If you use other systems, you have to compile the programs for your environment.
